name: Regina Bella
description: I am completely okay to move in the future to any country where my beloved is. I am a family-oriented and loyal woman who can always be not only a good lover but who likes to discover new things with my man and wants to be a partner and a friend. I believe in God not crazy but I try to attend church twice a month and I want my man to follow at least ten commandments and bring up our kids according to normal moral values. And by the way if you have kids – I will accept them with pleasure! It seems to you that I am young but you can try to write me and you will see much more mature woman than you expected.
